Class DataIDLabel

java.lang.Object
  jam.io.hdf.DataObject
      jam.io.hdf.DataIDLabel
public class DataIDLabel
extends DataObject

Class to represent an HDF Data identifier label data object. The label is meant to be a short probably one or 2 word label.
